-- Renewable Energy Generation Buys Cornwall County Wind Farm for $4 Million
-- Todd White
-- 2010-06-14T06:24:49Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-14/renewable-energy-generation-buys-cornwall-county-wind-farm-for-4-million.html

          
          
             Renewable Energy Generation Ltd.
said it bought a 4.95-megawatt wind farm in Cornwall county for
2.8 million pounds from E.ON Climate and Renewables UK
Operations Ltd., according to a regulatory filing by the U.K.
company. As much as 1.2 million pounds more may be paid subject
to the project receiving planning permission to repower the
site, the statement said.  
          
          


  


        